      <title>印度 11 月份工业产出增至六个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-s-industrial-output-grows-to-six-month-high-in-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度11月份工厂产量升至六个月来的最高水平，增强了人们对部分经济领域将出现反弹的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-s-industrial-output-grows-to-six-month-high-in-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
