    <item>
      <title>Pimco 称英国政府不太可能改变财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/pimco-uk-government-unlikely-to-change-fiscal-rules-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pimco 经济学家 Peder Beck-Friis 表示，他预计市场将在未来几个月内消化英国“财政可信度的提升”，并且英国政府债券收益率在曲线前端看起来“相当有吸引力”。他在彭博电视上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/pimco-uk-government-unlikely-to-change-fiscal-rules-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前英格兰银行官员称里夫斯可能不得不放弃税收承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/reeves-may-scrap-tax-pledge-says-ex-bank-of-england-official-martin-weale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行前利率制定员马丁·威尔表示，如果市场利率进一步上升，英国工党政府可能不得不放弃不提高劳动人民税收的宣言承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/reeves-may-scrap-tax-pledge-says-ex-bank-of-england-official-martin-weale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Quanterix 接近以全股票形式收购 Akoya Biosciences</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/quanterix-is-close-to-nears-175-million-deal-for-akoya-bioscience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Quanterix Corp. 正就以全股票交易的方式收购生命科学同行 Akoya Biosciences Inc. 进行深入谈判，这可能会将两家检测不同发展阶段疾病的公司合并起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/quanterix-is-close-to-nears-175-million-deal-for-akoya-bioscience</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国市场稍事休息，收益率徘徊在十年高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/uk-markets-get-reprieve-with-yields-stuck-near-decade-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于英国债券和货币交易员来说，忙碌的一周即将结束，收益率徘徊在多年来的最高水平附近，英镑则接近 2023 年底以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/uk-markets-get-reprieve-with-yields-stuck-near-decade-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 09:30:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险缓解，欧洲天然气价格或将迎来一个月来首次周度下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/european-gas-set-for-first-weekly-drop-in-a-month-as-risks-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对市场供应的担忧有所缓解，欧洲天然气价格有望出现自 12 月中旬以来的首次周度下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/european-gas-set-for-first-weekly-drop-in-a-month-as-risks-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 08:16:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市下跌，因交易员在薪资数据公布前寻求庇护：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五股市和债市下跌，因交易员在美国就业数据公布前采取谨慎态度，该数据将为经济状况和利率前景提供新的见解。]]></description>
